title: Pupu Kitchen and Health Food Shop
description: Macrobiotic cafe connected to a health food store. Feels like you're in someone's kitchen that's decorated with a Hawaiian touch. The Japanese set lunch costs around 1000 yen. Also offers desserts; try the chocolate cake. You can shop while you wait for your order. Address in Japanese: 〒451-0031 名古屋市西区城西2丁目15番地13号.
streetAddress: Yubinbango 451-0031 Nagoya, Nishi-ku, Josai 2-chome, number 15 No. 13
